@startuml
title Communication Diagram - UC003 Đăng nhập mạng xã hội

allow_mixing
actor "Guest" as Actor
boundary "LoginUI" as UI
control "OAuthProvider" as Provider
control "AuthController" as Controller
entity "UserAccount" as UserDB

Actor -right-> UI : 1: Select OAuth
UI -right-> Provider : 2: Request Auth
Actor -down-> Provider : 3: Grant Permission
Provider -down-> Controller : 4: Callback with Data
Controller -left-> UserDB : 5: Check/Create User
Controller -up-> UI : 6: Success Token
@enduml